---
// Quickstart Guide
import { Code } from 'astro:components';
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Quickstart - FlagLite</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0a0a0a;
      --fg: #fafafa;
      --muted: #a1a1aa;
      --accent: #3b82f6;
      --code-bg: #18181b;
      --border: #27272a;
    }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--fg);
      line-height: 1.7;
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem; }
    p { margin: 1rem 0; color: var(--muted); }
    pre { background: var(--code-bg); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; overflow-x: auto; margin: 1rem 0; }
    code { font-family: 'SF Mono', Consolas, monospace; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .lead { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--fg); }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
    th, td { text-align: left; padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    th { color: var(--fg); }
    td { color: var(--muted); }
    td code { background: var(--code-bg); padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem; border-radius: 4px; }
    .back { margin-bottom: 2rem; display: inline-block; }
    hr { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 2rem 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a href="/" class="back">← Back to FlagLite</a>
  
  <h1>Quickstart</h1>
  <p class="lead">Get feature flags running in 5 minutes.</p>
  
  <hr>
  
  <h2>1. Install the CLI</h2>
  <Code code="curl -fsSL https://flaglite.dev/install.sh | sh" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
  
  <p><strong>Alternatives:</strong></p>
  <Code code={`# npm
npm install -g flaglite

# cargo
cargo install flaglite`} lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
  
  <p>Verify installation:</p>
  <Code code="flaglite --version" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
  
  <hr>
  
  <h2>2. Create an Account</h2>
  <Code code="flaglite signup" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
  <p>This creates your account with an auto-generated username (like <code>brave-otter</code>). No email required.</p>
  
  <p>Already have an account?</p>
  <Code code="flaglite login" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
  
  <hr>
  
  <h2>3. Create a Flag</h2>
  <Code code="flaglite flags create my-feature" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
  <p>Output:</p>
  <Code code="✓ Flag 'my-feature' created (disabled)" lang="text" theme="github-dark" />
  <p>Flags start <strong>disabled</strong> by default.</p>
  
  <hr>
  
  <h2>4. Toggle the Flag</h2>
  <Code code="flaglite flags toggle my-feature" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
  <p>Output:</p>
  <Code code="✓ Flag 'my-feature' is now ENABLED" lang="text" theme="github-dark" />
  
  <hr>
  
  <h2>5. Use in Your Code</h2>
  <p>Set your API key:</p>
  <Code code="export FLAGLITE_API_KEY=flg_xxxxxxxx" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
  
  <h3>JavaScript</h3>
  <Code code="npm install flaglite" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
  <Code code={`import flags from 'flaglite'

if (await flags.enabled('my-feature')) {
  // New feature code
}`} lang="javascript" theme="github-dark" />
  
  <h3>Python</h3>
  <Code code="pip install flaglite" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
  <Code code={`from flaglite import FlagLite

flags = FlagLite()

if await flags.enabled('my-feature'):
    # New feature code`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />
  
  <h3>Go</h3>
  <Code code="go get github.com/faiscadev/flaglite-go" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
  <Code code={`import "github.com/faiscadev/flaglite-go"

client := flaglite.New()

if client.Enabled("my-feature") {
    // New feature code
}`} lang="go" theme="github-dark" />
  
  <h3>Rust</h3>
  <Code code="cargo add flaglite" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
  <Code code={`use flaglite::FlagLite;

let client = FlagLite::new()?;

if client.enabled("my-feature").await {
    // New feature code
}`} lang="rust" theme="github-dark" />
  
  <hr>
  
  <h2>Quick Reference</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Command</th><th>Description</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>flaglite signup</code></td><td>Create an account</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>flaglite login</code></td><td>Log in to existing account</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>flaglite flags create &lt;name&gt;</code></td><td>Create a new flag</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>flaglite flags list</code></td><td>List all flags</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>flaglite flags toggle &lt;name&gt;</code></td><td>Toggle a flag on/off</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>flaglite flags get &lt;name&gt;</code></td><td>Get flag status</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  
  <hr>
  
  <p>Need help? <a href="https://github.com/faiscadev/flaglite">GitHub</a></p>
</body>
</html>
